data.title: milConnect: Benefits and Records for DoD Affiliates
data.meta_description: Manage contact information, check records and benefits
data.text:
Browser Requirements

Internet Explorer is no longer supported.

For best viewing results, use Microsoft Edge, Firefox, or Chrome.

Need help getting a compatible browser?

Please call the DMDC Support Center (DSC) at (800) 477-8227 for 24/7 technical support.

Want assistance with your benefits by phone?

Please call the DMDC/DEERS Support Office (DSO) at (800) 538-9552. You can speak to a customer service representative between 8:00 a.m. and 8:00 p.m. Eastern time.
